metadata.name: Krystexxa 8 mg ml Injection solution concentrate

clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: For use in the treatment of constipation in the absence of bowel obstruction and for surgical preparation of the colon L926

contraindications.pharmacodynamics: Bisoxatin is a stimulant laxative which increases peristalsis and inhibits the absorbtion of water and ions in the intestine L926 This increases the water content of the feces and increases its movement through the intestine
